---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Siding Installation',
  provider: { '@type': 'GeneralContractor', name: 'Purpose Construction', url: 'https://purposeconstructionco.com' },
  areaServed: { '@type': 'State', name: 'Texas', containedIn: { '@type': 'Country', name: 'United States' } },
  description: 'Siding installation across East Texas — fiber cement, LP SmartSide, vinyl, and engineered wood siding with soffit, fascia, and house wrap for East Texas homes.',
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Siding Installation East Texas | Purpose Construction"
  description="Siding installation across East Texas — fiber cement, LP SmartSide, vinyl, and engineered wood with soffit and fascia. Purpose Construction serves East Texas homeowners. Call (936) 555-5555."
  schema={schema}
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Services', href: '/services' }, { label: 'Exterior Services', href: '/exterior-services' }, { label: 'Siding Installation', href: '/siding-installation' }]} />
  <PageHero title="Siding Installation in East Texas" subtitle="Fiber cement, LP SmartSide, vinyl, and engineered wood siding installed with proper house wrap, soffit, fascia, and trim for lasting exterior protection." tag="Exterior Service" />

  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-50">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <SectionHeading tag="Siding Installation" title="Siding That Protects Against East Texas Elements" />
          <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600">
            <p>East Texas's combination of high humidity, heavy rainfall, and pine tree pollen creates a harsh environment for exterior siding. Products that perform well in dry climates can fail quickly in the Piney Woods — warping, rotting at the bottom courses, or delaminating at seams within a few years. Purpose Construction specifies siding products that are proven in humid Southern climates, with fiber cement and LP SmartSide being our primary recommendations for longevity in the Lufkin area.</p>
            <p>Proper house wrap installation is just as important as the siding product itself. We install continuous water-resistive barriers with lapped and taped seams at penetrations, so moisture that gets behind the siding has a drainage plane to exit rather than absorbing into your sheathing and framing. This detail is often skipped in lower-quality installations and is the primary cause of long-term moisture problems behind siding.</p>
            <p>We replace storm-damaged siding, re-side entire homes, and install siding on new construction and additions across East Texas and Angelina County — matching profiles and textures where needed for seamless repairs and upgrades.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
            <a href="/exterior-services" class="btn-outline">All Exterior Services</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="https://placehold.co/640x480/2a2520/555?text=Siding+Installation" alt="Siding installation across East Texas by Purpose Construction" class="rounded-xl shadow-hero" width="640" height="480" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-white border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="What's Included" title="Siding Installation Services" align="center" />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
        {['Fiber Cement Siding', 'LP SmartSide', 'Vinyl Siding', 'Engineered Wood', 'Soffit & Fascia', 'Trim', 'House Wrap', 'Storm Damage Replacement'].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>{item}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding-sm bg-warm-50 border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="Related Services" title="Related Exterior Services" />
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {[{ label: 'Exterior Painting', href: '/exterior-painting' }, { label: 'Window Installation', href: '/window-installation' }, { label: 'Exterior Services', href: '/exterior-services' }].map(link => (
          <a href={link.href} class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700 shadow-card hover:border-brand-red-mid hover:text-charcoal-900 transition-all duration-200">{link.label} →</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-red">
    <div class="container-mid px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="display-md text-white mb-4">Upgrade Your Home's Exterior</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-base text-white/80">Contact Purpose Construction for a free siding estimate. We serve Lufkin and all of East Texas.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost px-8 py-4">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:9365555555" class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150">(936) 555-5555</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
